        "html": "=<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n  <style>\n    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; }\n    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }\n    .header { background: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }\n    .content { padding: 20px; background: #f9f9f9; }\n    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background: #4CAF50; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"header\">\n      <h1>✅ 审核通过</h1>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content\">\n      <h2>亲爱的 {{ $json.userName }}，</h2>\n      <p>好消息！您的门户申请已经通过审核。</p>\n      <p><strong>门户名称：</strong>{{ $json.userName }}</p>\n      <p><strong>审核时间：</strong>{{ $json.timestamp }}</p>\n      <p>您现在可以访问和管理您的门户了。</p>\n      <p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;\">\n        <a href=\"https://your-platform.com/portal/{{ $json.portalId }}\" class=\"button\">查看我的门户</a>\n      </p>\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 14px;\">\n        如有任何问题，请随时联系我们的客服团队。\n      </p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</body>\n</html>",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "send-approval-email",
      "name": "Send Approval Email",
